  "doc_id": "20365",
  "text": "This study presents the first published results on the effects of SCE on postprandial blood glucose and insulin response in healthy people. The doses of the herbal extract had significant effects on postprandial insulinemia after administration with sucrose solution. The doses of extract for this study are lower than the 1000 mg dose found to be efficacious in other Salacia extracts species studies [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
